column2: Do Not Track Disclosure : The JibJab Sites do not currently respond to "Do Not Track" signals of Web browsers. However, should the industry establish uniform technological standards for recognizing and interpreting "Do Not Track" signals, the JibJab Sites would be open to following such industry standards.
